<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Trading Tracker — Analysez vos trades, progressez plus vite</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0d1117;
            --bg-card: #161b22;
            --bg-card2: #1c2230;
            --accent: #3b82f6;
            --accent-2: #10b981;
            --accent-glow: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
            --text-main: #f0f6fc;
            --text-muted: #8b949e;
            --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ── NAVBAR ─────────────────────────────────── */
        .landing-nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .nav-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-brand .brand-icon {
            width: 34px; height: 34px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .nav-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .btn-login {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            padding: 0.45rem 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-main);
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-login:hover {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .btn-cta-nav {
            padding: 0.45rem 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-cta-nav:hover {
            background: #2563eb;
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* ── HERO ────────────────────────────────────── */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 8rem 1.5rem 4rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -200px; left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 800px; height: 800px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.3);
            color: #60a5fa;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.15;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            max-width: 760px;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }

        .hero h1 .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn-hero-primary {
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            transition: all 0.25s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(59,130,246,0.35);
        }

        .btn-hero-primary:hover {
            background: #2563eb;
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 36px rgba(59,130,246,0.5);
        }

        .btn-hero-secondary {
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }

        .btn-hero-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        /* ── STATS STRIP ─────────────────────────────── */
        .stats-strip {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 3rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-item .stat-num {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .stat-item .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 0.2rem;
        }

        /* ── FEATURES ────────────────────────────────── */
        .section {
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .section-sub {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.25rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.75rem;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.3);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(59,130,246,0.1);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            width: 44px; height: 44px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        .feature-icon.blue { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12); color: #60a5fa; }
        .feature-icon.green { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.12); color: #34d399; }
        .feature-icon.purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.12); color: #a78bfa; }
        .feature-icon.orange { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); color: #fbbf24; }
        .feature-icon.red { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.12); color: #f87171; }
        .feature-icon.teal { background: rgba(20,184,166,0.12); color: #2dd4bf; }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ── HOW IT WORKS ────────────────────────────── */
        .steps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .step-num {
            width: 48px; height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
            color: #fff;
        }

        .step h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .step p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ── METRICS PREVIEW ─────────────────────────── */
        .metrics-preview {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .metric-box {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            background: var(--bg-card2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .metric-value {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .metric-value.positive { color: var(--accent-2); }
        .metric-value.negative { color: #f87171; }
        .metric-value.neutral { color: var(--accent); }

        .metric-label {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
        }

        /* ── CTA BANNER ──────────────────────────────── */
        .cta-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59,130,246,0.15), rgba(16,185,129,0.1));
            border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 5rem 1.5rem;
        }

        .cta-banner h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-banner p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* ── FOOTER ──────────────────────────────────── */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover { color: var(--text-main); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <nav class="landing-nav">
        <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}" class="nav-brand">
            <div class="brand-icon">
                <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
            </div>
            Trading Tracker
        </a>

        <div class="nav-actions">
            <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn-login">
                <i class="bi bi-person-circle"></i>
                Se connecter
            </a>
            <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="btn-cta-nav">
                Commencer gratuitement
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-badge">
            <i class="bi bi-stars"></i>
            Journal de trading professionnel
        </div>

        <h1>
            Analysez vos trades.<br>
            <span class="highlight">Progressez plus vite.</span>
        </h1>

        <p>
            Enregistrez chaque trade, identifiez vos patterns, suivez vos statistiques
            et devenez le trader que vous voulez être.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="btn-hero-primary">
                Commencer gratuitement <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
            <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn-hero-secondary">
                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right"></i> Se connecter
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STATS STRIP -->
    <div class="stats-strip">
        <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-num">100%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Données privées</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Trades enregistrables</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-num">7+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Métriques analysées</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-num">0€</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Pour commencer</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FEATURES -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-label">Fonctionnalités</div>
        <div class="section-title">Tout ce dont vous avez besoin</div>
        <p class="section-sub">Des outils pensés pour les traders sérieux qui veulent progresser avec méthode.</p>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon blue"><i class="bi bi-journal-text"></i></div>
                <h3>Journal de trades</h3>
                <p>Enregistrez chaque trade avec ses paramètres : actif, R/R, confluences, setup, erreurs. Gardez une trace complète de votre activité.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon green"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line"></i></div>
                <h3>Statistiques avancées</h3>
                <p>Win rate, gain moyen en R, performance par timeframe ou confluence. Visualisez vos forces et vos faiblesses en un coup d'œil.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon purple"><i class="bi bi-images"></i></div>
                <h3>Screenshots annotés</h3>
                <p>Attachez vos captures d'entrée, de gestion et de clôture à chaque trade pour une revue visuelle de votre exécution.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon orange"><i class="bi bi-funnel"></i></div>
                <h3>Filtres & confluences</h3>
                <p>Créez vos propres confluences et setups, filtrez vos statistiques pour comprendre ce qui fonctionne vraiment dans votre edge.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon teal"><i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i></div>
                <h3>Analyse temporelle</h3>
                <p>Identifiez vos meilleures sessions par jour de la semaine, par créneau horaire et par timeframe d'analyse.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon red"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle"></i></div>
                <h3>Suivi des erreurs</h3>
                <p>Catégorisez vos erreurs de trading pour identifier les patterns négatifs récurrents et éliminer vos biais comportementaux.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- METRICS PREVIEW -->
    <div class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
        <div class="section-label">Aperçu</div>
        <div class="section-title">Des métriques claires</div>
        <p class="section-sub">Suivez votre évolution avec les indicateurs qui comptent vraiment.</p>

        <div class="metrics-preview">
            <div class="metric-box">
                <div class="metric-value positive">68%</div>
                <div class="metric-label">Win Rate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-box">
                <div class="metric-value positive">+2.4R</div>
                <div class="metric-label">Gain moyen</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-box">
                <div class="metric-value negative">-0.8R</div>
                <div class="metric-label">Perte moyenne</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-box">
                <div class="metric-value neutral">1:3.2</div>
                <div class="metric-label">R/R moyen</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-box">
                <div class="metric-value positive">+47R</div>
                <div class="metric-label">Profit factor</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-label">Comment ça marche</div>
        <div class="section-title">Simple, rapide, efficace</div>
        <p class="section-sub">Commencez à analyser vos trades en moins de 5 minutes.</p>

        <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <h3>Créez votre compte</h3>
                <p>Inscription gratuite et immédiate, sans carte bancaire requise.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <h3>Configurez votre setup</h3>
                <p>Ajoutez vos timeframes, confluences et types de trades personnalisés.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <h3>Enregistrez vos trades</h3>
                <p>Saisissez chaque trade avec ses screenshots et paramètres de risk management.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">4</div>
                <h3>Analysez & progressez</h3>
                <p>Consultez vos statistiques, identifiez vos patterns et améliorez votre edge.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA BANNER -->
    <div style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="cta-banner">
            <h2>Prêt à trader avec méthode ?</h2>
            <p>Rejoignez les traders qui analysent leurs performances et progressent chaque jour.</p>
            <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="btn-hero-primary">
                Créer mon compte gratuitement <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
        <p>
            &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Trading Tracker &nbsp;·&nbsp;
            <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}">Connexion</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
            <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}">Inscription</a>
        </p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>